<taxonomicNameLabel pageId="1" pageNumber="68">sp. n.</taxonomicNameLabel>
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 1–9" captionStartId="F1" captionText="Figures 1 - 9. Aspilota stigmalis sp. n.: 1 scape, pedicel and flagellomeres 1 - 2 2 head in dorsal view 3 mandible 4 paraclypeal pit 5 propodeum 6 hind femur 7 distal part of right fore wing 8 first discal cell of fore wing 9 tergites 1 - 3." httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/11529" pageId="1" pageNumber="68">Figures 1-9</figureCitation>
